lead_paragraph: Louis Oosthuizen made another fast start to his first tournament of the year, shooting a 7-under 65 in the first round of the Qatar Masters to share the lead with Pablo Larrazabal on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Oosthuizen Shares Lead With Larrazabal in Qatar
